      "biography": "<p>Demonstrates the <strong>Dual Weapon</strong> style (+1 to melee attack throws for the second weapon, +1 more from Specialization) and <strong>Weapon Finesse</strong> (DEX replaces STR on the attack throw). In leather and without a shield, the armour-gated thief skills (Backstabbing, Hiding, Pickpocketing, Sneaking) remain available — equip a shield and the module flags them as blocked.</p>"
